    "description": "We at Zomato Holdings Services are looking for an experienced Backend Developer based out of Ranchi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Zomato Holdings Services:\nZomato Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zomato Holdings Services!",
